    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you should expect some minor oil seepage and a suspension that feels a bit soft. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior shows moderate wear on the upholstery and some fading on the dashboard. It recently passed inspection, but will likely need new tires and a brake service within the next few thousand miles. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
