      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's ready to hit the road with a new owner right away! If you\u2019re looking for a reliable ride that still looks great and runs smoothly, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by for a test drive\u2014I\u2019d love to show it to you!",
      "price": 32500.0,
