    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a driver seeking a reliable, well-maintained car that still presents beautifully. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, though it shows minor, honest signs of road use such as small stone chips on the hood. Inside, the cabin is a testament to careful ownership: the leather upholstery remains supple and free of tears, the carpets are clean, and it has never been smoked in. All onboard electronics, including the premium sound system and navigation, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; it starts eagerly, idles smoothly, and the transmission provides crisp, seamless shifts. We have recently completed a full service, including a synthetic oil change and a brake system check, so it is ready for your next road trip without any immediate investment required. This is a solid, honest car that looks great in a driveway and performs even better on the open road.",
